	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107418772468778839">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://glennf.com/">Glenn Fleishman. Unsolicited Pundit</a>.&nbsp; Glenn operates the www.isbn.nu experiment and is also based here in Seattle.&nbsp; I like how he set up his site entrance and also all of the activities he links to.&nbsp; Something to do for an orcmid.com facelift and also new entrances to NuovoDoc and nfoWare.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107418772468778839">Thursday, January 15, 2004</a></span></div>
