	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107386409965884801">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.msu.edu/user/abbottb/formal.htm">The formal approach to meaning</a>.&nbsp; I wasn't looking for this.  It popped up in a search for something else.&nbsp; I definitely want to return to it for a closer look.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107386409965884801">Sunday, January 11, 2004</a></span></div>
