	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107386288950377867">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://hci.stanford.edu/winograd/publications.html">Terry Winograd publications</a>.&nbsp; I blogged this because there are a bunch of broken links on Winograd material that use www-pcd.stanford.edu, apparently a defunct server.  <br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107386288950377867">Sunday, January 11, 2004</a></span></div>
